track_notes: Standard trail from the valley nearby Grän to Mt. Aggenstein via Bad Kissinger hut.

track_title: Ascent/transit from top station of Füssener Jöchle gondola

track_notes: This ascent is a narrow zig zag trail in the upper part that is impressive when seen from far. Descend first some metres to start the ascent then through a rockier part with steel ropes. Unites with the trail from Austria just below the summit. Further supporting steel ropes to the summit.
track_title: Ascent from top station of Hochalpbahn chair lift from Germany
